"79:34:3" : {s: 79, a: 34, w: 3, r: "طمم", t: "ٱلطَّآمَّةُ", l: "طَّآمَّة", lc: 1, tl: "l-ṭāmatu", lb: "মহাবিপদ, মহাপ্রলয়, কেয়ামত",e: "the Overwhelming Calamity", b: "মহাবিপদ, মহা বিপর্যয়", f: 1, rm: "to cover up, overflow, overwhelm, swallow up, fill to the brim. taammatun - calamity, overwhelming event."},
